{"type": "article", "id": 14545, "title": "铜质咖啡器皿", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-07T07:00:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060600032821Qlp5wyRV7Hz3JO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t今年的巴黎家居装饰博览会上，英国设计品牌 tom dixon 带来了一套名为“ brew ”的铜质的咖啡器皿。包括饼干罐、咖啡罐、咖啡杯、咖啡勺、咖啡壶、牛奶锅、咖啡机和托盘等 8 件，涵盖了咖啡从储存到加热冲泡再到品尝的全过程，非常完整。铜质的外形具有强烈的光泽，带来一种坚固的金属感，而内部的拉丝钢面也体现出精细的做工。杯盖或底部印有“ tom dixon london ”，是咖啡爱好者收藏必备。<a href=\"http://www.tomdixon.net/uk/brew.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142031d37j50YyzDJsu24T.jpg\" width=\"783\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6385696\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142031ZJh0d1qzWvrsX2Mf.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"634\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.77506112\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142032iof3W1npbeY0aztw.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"592\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142032LUorxa9h2YQPkcI4.jpg\" width=\"817\" height=\"613\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.750306\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142032HS0k1CWofViEZzjQ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"614\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142033aDU0IJBEciPWhb7l.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"618\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75550122\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}